---
title: Chicken and Chorizo Rice with roasted tomatoes and bell peppers
description: This Iberian-inspired rice is full of savoury flavours. Softened bell peppers, bursting cherry tomatoes, succulent chicken, and spicy chorizo all fight for top billing in this jam-packed and delicious dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R01_W04_IE_IEXCC0061-2_KB_Main_high-640555b2.jpg
